caption: The image features a heart-shaped sign with the words "I Love Zoom Classes" written on it. The sign is surrounded by various school supplies, including a backpack, a bottle, a book, and a pair of scissors. The backpack is located on the left side of the sign, while the bottle is positioned to the right of the sign. The book is situated below the sign, and the pair of scissors is placed above the book. The scene conveys a sense of excitement and enthusiasm for online classes.
original_title: Pink And Yellow Minimalist I Love Zoom Class Poster
